<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">Help & Documentation</h1>

  <div class="space-y-10">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 border-b pb-2">Getting Started</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
        <p><strong>1. Browse Cars:</strong> Navigate to the Cars page to see all available ads. You can sort them by price or year.</p>
